{"article_id":"0E1yEgPnwCXBD2UQ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump has repeatedly insisted","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that there was no \" collusion \" between his campaign and the Russian government","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to influence the 2016 election .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"But a major new report from the New York Times reveals","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that Trump ' s son Donald Trump Jr. , the president ' s son-in-law Jared Kushner , and his former campaign chair Paul Manafort all met with a Kremlin-tied Russian lawyer","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"- because Trump Jr. was told","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"she might have dirt on Hillary Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Times reporters Jo Becker , Matt Apuzzo , and Adam Goldman first revealed the existence of the June 9 , 2016 , Trump Tower meeting in a Saturday story ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and followed up Sunday with the added scoop","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that the Russian lawyer had promised to reveal damaging information about Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Trump Jr. is claiming","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that the lawyer did not in fact have any useful information","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"and that the matter progressed no further","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"- and that Trump himself had no knowledge of the meeting at all .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Still , Trump Jr. has already changed his story about this meeting several times","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"first claiming","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"he had no such meeting ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"then claiming","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"it was about the topic of Russian adoptions ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and only now admitting","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"he agreed to take it","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"because an \" acquaintance \"","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"he met","depth":15},{"id":24,"text":"when Trump ' s Miss Universe pageant was held in Moscow","depth":15},{"id":25,"text":"told him","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"this person \" might have information helpful to the campaign . \"","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"This report comes","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"after a pair of Wall Street Journal scoops","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"revealing","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that a Republican operative contacted Russian hackers in an effort","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"to obtain Hillary Clinton ' s deleted emails","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"- and that the operative suggested","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that Trump adviser Michael Flynn was involved with his effort .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Together , these stories provide our first real indications","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that high-level people on Trump ' s team attempted to work with people","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"tied to the Russian government","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to get information","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that could impact the campaign","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"and hurt Clinton ' s chances .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"However , there is still no outright proof","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that these efforts progressed beyond initial inquiries","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and resulted in some type of mutual coordination or collaboration .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"It is also not clear","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"that this Russian lawyer , Natalia Veselnitskaya , was acting at the Russian government ' s behest .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"The big picture , though , is that the president ' s dismissals of the very idea","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that his campaign coordinated with Russians","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"look ever tougher to take at face value .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"These stories suggest","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"that many of his top advisers were certainly open to the idea of collusion .","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"What , if anything , they actually ended up doing , though , remains unknown","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"- and is the topic of special counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation .","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"The context and specifics of this curious , newly revealed meeting","depth":3},{"id":53,"text":"In early May , Trump drove his two remaining opponents out of the Republican presidential nomination contest ,","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"setting him up to advance to the general election ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"where he was near certain to face Hillary Clinton .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Then on June 9 , 2016 , Donald Trump Jr. , campaign chair Paul Manafort , and campaign adviser","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"( and Trump son-in-law )","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Jared Kushner met at Trump Tower with Natalia Veselnitskaya , a Russian lawyer .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Veselnitskaya has represented state-owned businesses ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"and the Times characterizes her as \" a formidable operator with a history","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"of pushing the Kremlin ' s agenda . \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Five anonymous sources","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"interviewed by the Times ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"including three White House advisers ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"say","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Trump Jr. was specifically told beforehand","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that the meeting would yield damaging information about Hillary Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Trump Jr. ' s newest statement claims","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that the meeting came about","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"because an \" acquaintance \"","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"he met in connection with the 2013 Miss Universe pageant","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"( which was held in Moscow )","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"asked him to meet with a person","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"who could have \" information helpful to the campaign , \"","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"and that he was not told in advance whom he ' d be meeting with .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"The statement also says","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that Trump Jr. asked Manafort and Kushner to attend the meeting","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"but \" told them nothing of the substance . \"","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"The account of the president ' s son goes on to state","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"that in the meeting , Veselnitskaya claimed to have \" information","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"that individuals","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"connected to Russia","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"were funding the Democratic National Committee","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"and supporting Ms. Clinton , \"","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"but that \" her statements were vague , ambiguous , and made no sense . \"","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Then ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"he claims ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Veselnitskaya began discussing a controversy","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"involving the Magnitsky Act","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"- a US law","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"attempting to penalize Russian human rights abusers -","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"and the Russian government ' s subsequent retaliatory decision","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"to ban all US adoption of Russian children .","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"( Veselnitskaya has lobbied for repeal of the Magnitsky Act for years . )","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"Trump Jr. then says","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"he concluded","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that the promise of \" helpful information \" was merely a \" pretext \"","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"to get him in the room","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"to discuss the Magnitsky Act and the adoption controversy .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"And that ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"he says ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"is the end of the story .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Donald Trump Jr. keeps changing his story about the meeting","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"One of the most suspicious elements of this meeting is that the president ' s son keeps changing his account of it .","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"In March , Donald Jr. told the Times","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that he ' d never had a meeting with Russians","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"that was set up","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"or in which he was representing the campaign :","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Did I meet with people","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"that were Russian ?","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"I ' m sure ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"I ' m sure","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"I did .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"... But none","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"that were set up .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"None","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"that I can think of at the moment .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"And certainly none","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"that I was representing the campaign in any way , shape or form .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"Then in the Times ' s Saturday report","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"revealing the meeting ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"Donald Jr. was quoted","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"suddenly remembering the meeting","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"- but in his telling ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"it was \" primarily \" about adoption policy .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"It was a short introductory meeting .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"I asked Jared and Paul to stop by .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"We primarily discussed a program about the adoption of Russian children","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"that was active and popular with American families years ago","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"and was since ended by the Russian government ,","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"but it was not a campaign issue at the time","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"and there was no follow up . ...","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"I was asked to attend the meeting by an acquaintance ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"but was not told the name of the person","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"I would be meeting with beforehand .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"when the Times obtained additional information","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"suggesting","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"that the purpose of the meeting was to obtain information","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"that could damage Hillary Clinton ,","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"Donald Jr. finally admitted","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"that , yes , that was true ,","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"but argued","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"that it went nowhere ,","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"and finally laid out what is","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"( for now )","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"his full account ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"which I ' ve quoted in the previous section .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"How this changes what we know about Trump ' s team and Russia","depth":4},{"id":150,"text":"There ' s long been a whole lot of evidence","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"that several Trump associates had ties to Russian officials ,","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"and of course it was clear that Trump ' s public policies were far more pro-Russia than the Republican norm .","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"But for a long while , there really wasn ' t any hard evidence","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"tying anyone in Trumpworld to any collusion or attempted collusion","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"to influence the 2016 election -","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"making it plausible that the Russian influence campaign and hackings were done","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"without any involvement from Trump associates .","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"That changed , first , with the scoop from the Wall Street Journal ' s Shane Harris","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"that the late GOP operative Peter Smith reached out to Russian hackers","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"to try to get Hillary Clinton ' s deleted emails from them","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"- and that he had claimed to be working with Michael Flynn in that endeavor .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"( It ' s not yet clear","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"whether Flynn was involved ,","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"and he hasn ' t commented on the matter one way or the other . )","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"Now , we learn","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"that the president ' s son , son-in-law , and campaign chair took a meeting with a Russian lawyer in the hopes","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"of dredging up some sort of dirt on Hillary Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"So there are now more indications","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"that many of Trump ' s top people were at least open to collaborating with Russians on anti-Clinton shenanigans of some kind .","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"Still , it remains unclear whether any sort of collaborative effort ended up materializing in the end .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":341,"left":222,"right":340,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":218,"right":221,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":197,"right":217,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":177,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":173,"right":176,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":173,"left":0,"right":172,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":174,"right":175,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":175,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":196,"left":179,"right":195,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":179,"left":7,"right":178,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":182,"right":194,"relation":"adversative","